release.body:
<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at 3.9.x -->

## What's Changed
### Dependency Upgrades 🚀
* Update netty monorepo to v4.1.92.Final by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9277
* Bump micronaut-maven-plugin to 3.5.4 (#9370)
* Bump micronaut-servlet to 3.3.7 (#9398)
* Bump micronaut-aws to 3.17.3 (#9368)

### Tests ✅
* test: Writable in Controller and Filter by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9286
* TCK Test for JSON additional types codec by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9272
* Remove test limitation for TCK by @timyates in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9317
* Add test for `@Body` not being required in 3.9.x by @timyates in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9318
* TCK tests for boolean textplain and default media type for String return type by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9314

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/compare/v3.9.2...v3.9.3
